The 43-year-old, who gave birth to daughter Vale on August 13, 2014, drew plenty of attention in her $550 Cushnie Et Ochs figure-hugging long-sleeved crop top, which featured cut-outs down each of the arms, and black A-line skirt, which fell just below her knees.

Despite being on the red carpet primarily to interview the show's numerous celebrity attendees, Savannah was herself the talk of the town - particularly on Twitter, where fans were quick to compliment her on her new look. 

