Alongside a picture of herself and her Today show co-hosts, Al Roker, Matt Lauer and Carson Daly, posing on the red carpet, Savannah commented: 'A night to remember!' 

Indeed, it wasn't just Savannah's daring ensemble which Today show fans will be remembering for weeks to come; all four of the Today show hosts were left speechless after actor Jim Carrey asked Matt Lauer about the whereabouts of NBC anchor Brian Williams. 

'Where are you hiding Brian Williams?' the comedian asked, leaving both SNL host Tina Fey and Savannah struggling to string together a sentence, while 57-year-old Matt was only able to say: 'Look at the time!'

But happily for Mr Williams, the jokes at his expense were barely a fraction of the material on Sunday evening.

Musicians, actors, and politicians alike lined up on the red carpet to tell the Today show team just how much they love the show. 

